possie
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a place of shelter (in wartime)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:with /s/ or /z/
Notes: war time; sense of shelter as well as advantageous firing position; aka pozzy, posi, pozzie
Citations
